<item>
            <title>[WICKET-5234] OnEventHeaderItem can&apos;t be applied via AJAX</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-5234</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;OnEventHeaderItem doesn&apos;t have effect if it is applied to a component refreshed via AJAX. In short, OnEventHeaderItem is applied before the component is refreshed via AJAX, hence the releated event handler is removed from the target component. &lt;br/&gt;
We could modify JavaScript function Wicket.Ajax.Call.loadedCallback in order to apply header contributors after the component has been refreshed (see patch).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
